  <brief_title>Secondary Prevention of coRonary Events After Discharge From Hospital (SPREAD)</brief_title>
  <acronym>SPREAD</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Trial Comparing Post Discharge Interventions to Standard Care</official_title>
